rent lack of gamma-ray bright blazars at small\ncomoving frame viewing angles, if confirmed with larger samples, may suggest an\nintrinsic anisotropy or Lorentz factor dependence of the gamma-ray emission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Nov 2009 17:47:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Jan 2010 10:15:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-20"}
