 fatigue strongly\nsuggests that polarization fatigue in ferroelectrics is an interface effect,\nnot a bulk one.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Nov 2009 05:02:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-08-09"}
